OL,3,CBurglars targeted striker Isak during
OL,4,Cspree of high-value break-ins, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA gang of burglars targeted Premier
OL,8,FLeague star Alexander Isak as they
OL,9,Fcarried out a series of high-value
OL,10,Fbreak-ins, jurors were told.
OL,12,FThe Newcastle United and Sweden
OL,13,Fforward was the third victim of the
OL,14,Fgang who had already stolen jewellery
OL,15,Fand clothes worth more than #1 million
OL,16,Ffrom a Tyneside businesswoman, a court
OL,17,Fwas told on Tuesday (4 March).
