OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThree members of the same family,
OL,8,Fliving in Italy, have admitted
OL,9,Fconspiracy to commit burglary,
OL,10,FNewcastle Crown Court has heard.
OL,12,FBut a fourth family member, Valentino
OL,13,FNikolov, 32, denies the charge.
OL,15,FDan Cordey, prosecuting, said the
OL,16,FNewcastle United player's home in
OL,17,FDarras Hall was subjected to a break-
OL,18,Fin last April.
