OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe will outline more of the
OL,8,Fprosecution case about that on
OL,9,FWednesday (5 March).
OL,11,FEarlier, Mr Cordey said that the gang
OL,12,Farrived in the UK via a ferry from
OL,13,FCalais to Dover in a Citroen C3 and a
OL,14,FFord motorhome last March.
OL,16,FThey headed to London then drove to
OL,17,Fthe North East a few days later, Mr
OL,18,FCordey said.
