OL,4,Cspree of high-value break-ins, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe gang used the Citroen to travel to
OL,8,Fbreak-ins and the motorhome was a base
OL,9,Fwhere they slept, the prosecution said.
OL,11,FThe first burglary was at the home of
OL,12,FHelen and Michael McCardle in Jesmond,
OL,13,FNewcastle, on 30 March last year when
OL,14,Fthe couple were on holiday, Mr Cordey
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FThe gang stole her CBE medal, the
OL,18,Fprosecution said, as well as clothes,
OL,19,Fjewellery, gold coins and handbags
OL,20,Fworth more than #1 million.
