OL,4,Cspree of high-value break-ins, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FTwo days later the gang broke into the
OL,8,Fhome of Stephanie Stokoe, in Whitburn,
OL,9,FSunderland, and stole property
OL,10,Fincluding jewellery, designer handbags
OL,11,Fand shoes worth more than #100,000,
OL,12,Fthe prosecution said.
OL,14,FNikolov, of Tew Park Road, Birmingham,
OL,15,Fis representing himself at the trial
OL,16,Fand requires an Italian interpreter.
