OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FJurors have been told his brother
OL,8,FGiacomo Nikolov, 28, his sister Jela
OL,9,FJovanovic, 43, and her son Charlie
OL,10,FJovanovic, 23, who all reside in
OL,11,FItaly, have admitted conspiracy to
OL,12,Fcommit burglary.
OL,14,FSafet Ramic, who is the 58-year-old
OL,15,Ffather of Valentino Nikolov's former
OL,16,Fpartner, and who is from Winson
OL,17,FStreet, Birmingham, denies handling
OL,18,Fstolen goods.
OL,20,FThe prosecution will continue opening
OL,21,Fits case on Wednesday.
